==English==
===Adjective===
'''overladen''' 
# packed heavily, esp. beyond normal capacity; overloaded: ''a tray overladen with food'', ''a trunk overladen with clothes'' 
# burdened excessively: ''a student overladen with homework'', ''first-time parents overladen with new responsibility'' 

